[6/6/96 public]

I believe this problem is showing up because you have not run
dced_acl_patcher (located in /opt/dcelocal/etc). Please follow
the steps below before you try the above steps:

su as root
dce_login cell_admin ...
kill dced process and wait until it goes away
start dced with option -r, i.e., dced -r
wait for 30 seconds to let it get started
Run dced_acl_patcher, i.e., dced_acl_patcher (assuming its in your path)

I've marked this as a doc bug as it needs to be documented in 
proper places if not done already.

If dced_acl_patcher does not help then please change it back to code

